      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "The corn is withered.—",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The results of the terrible drought, coincident with the ravages of the locusts, are now described. The ancient versions present difficulty and variety in the exact rendering of this verse, owing to several words occurring in it being not found elsewhere in Holy Scripture. On the whole the English text seems correct and satisfactory.",
        "children": []
      },
